node.text:
Can you guess the origin of these ancient remains? 🔍

The first photo is of a raptor mummy wrapped in an elaborate herringbone pattern. At the head end, the remains of a car tonnage mask are visible.

All over the world, female archeologists are changing the face of history. We're highlighting trailblazing women in @the_explorers_club, from Easter Island to Egypt! 🗿🌏

Read the article: Discovery.com/farafield 

📷: Salima Ikram
